node.text: #Roomies, get into this! In April 2021, #MatthewZadokWilliams was fatally shot by police officers at his home near Decatur, Georgia. DeKalb County officials allege that he “lunged at officers with a knife on two separate occasions.” Months later, his mother and five sisters are still seeking justice for Matthew, who they say was having a mental health crisis. So, what’s really going on? #TSRInvestigates w/ #JustinCarter

node.title: The Police Shooting Death of Matthew Zadok Williams | TSR Investigates

node.text:
#PressPlay: Get y’all popcorn ready, Chance the Rapper’s new movie drops today in theaters across the country! “Chance the Rapper’s Magnificent Coloring World” marks the first time an artist has independently distributed a film to theatres.
________
“Magnificent Coloring World” is a concert film self-distributed through Chance the Rapper’s House of Kicks production company and film house.
________
Chance wrote, produced, edited and starred in the film, working hard this past year to bring never-before-seen footage to his fans. The footage was filmed in 2017 right before Chance took home 3 Grammys for his critically acclaimed mixtape “Coloring Book.”
________
Fans will be able to see the film in person for a limited time in several cities including Los Angeles, New York, Chicago, Detori, Las Vegas and Philly.

node.title: Chance The Rapper’s Film Released Today

node.text:
TSR STAFF: La’Janeé @_lajanee_
____________________ 
Recently, #NickiMinaj had a discussion with fans and #DojaCat’s new single, “Get Into It (Yuh)” was mentioned.
____________________
Explaining to fans why she didn’t join #DojaCat, though the latest single samples Nicki’s 2010 track, “Massive Attack,” she stated: “The truth is she asked me to get on that song. It’s not that I’m too busy at all.” 

Nicki added, “It’s just, there were middle people involved in that situation. So, I had told her if it was like how me and BIA were direct and we dealt with each other directly, it would be different. But I didn’t love that song because I didn’t think I could bring anything to it.”
____________________
Nicki explained that she requested another song to be sent to her. “So I asked them to send me something else. I think that was the second song they sent me, but I asked them to send me something else and they—Read more at theshaderoom.com. (📸:@gettyimages)
